      <title>风险上升 韩国计划设立基金保护供应链</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/south-korea-plans-fund-to-safeguard-supply-chains-as-risks-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国计划设立一只规模为 5 万亿韩元（36 亿美元）的基金，以减少对外国供应的依赖，以保护因地缘政治紧张局势而日益中断的供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/south-korea-plans-fund-to-safeguard-supply-chains-as-risks-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:36:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
